'''Turu-grass''' was a vegetal [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Shili/Legends|Shili]].

The wild scrub lands of Shili were covered with meter-high turu-grass, which was [[Color/Legends|red]] on one side and white on the other side. This color combination provided many species, including the [[Togruta]], with excellent cover and camouflage.
